{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 5}Then God brought him outside and said, \uc1\u8216*Look now toward heaven and count the stars, if you are able to count them! So will your descendants be.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 6}Abram believed in the {\scaps Lord}; and the {\scaps Lord} reckoned it to him as righteousness, {\super\cf2\fs24 7}and said to him, \uc1\u8216*I am the {\scaps Lord} who brought you out of Ur of the Chaldees, to give to you this land to inherit it.\uc1\u8217*
