{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 18}At that time the {\scaps Lord} made a solemn agreement with Abram, saying, \uc1\u8216*To your descendants I give this land, from the river of Egypt unto the great river, the river Euphrates.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 19}(This includes the lands of the Kenite, the Kenizzite, the Kadmonite, {\super\cf2\fs24 20}the Hittite, the Perizzite, the Rephaim, {\super\cf2\fs24 21}the Amorite, the Canaanite, the Girgashite, and Jebusite). 
