{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 15}He then blessed Joseph, saying, \uc1\u8216*The God whom my forefathers Abraham and Isaac revered and served, the God who has been my shepherd all my life long unto this day, {\super\cf2\fs24 16}the messenger who has delivered me from all evil, bless the boys; and let them be known as descendants of Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob; and let them grow into a multitude on the earth.\uc1\u8217*
