 {\super\cf2\fs24 12}While she continued praying before the {\scaps Lord}, Eli observed her mouth. {\super\cf2\fs24 13}Now Hannah was speaking to herself. Only her lips moved, but her voice was not heard; therefore Eli took her for a drunken woman. {\super\cf2\fs24 14}So Eli said to her, \uc1\u8216*How long will you act like a drunken woman? Put away the effects of your wine and go from the presence of the {\scaps Lord}.\uc1\u8217*
