{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 15}\uc1\u8216*No, my lord,\uc1\u8217* Hannah answered, \uc1\u8216*I am an unfortunate woman! I have drunk neither wine nor intoxicating drink, but I have been pouring out my heart before the {\scaps Lord}. {\super\cf2\fs24 16}Do not take your maid-servant to be a vile woman, for because of the greatness of my grief and vexation have I continued speaking until now.\uc1\u8217*
