{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 20}And Hannah conceived, and it came to pass at the coming around of the new year that she bore a son, and named him Samuel{\super\chftn}{\footnote\pard\plain\chftn   Heb: Asked of God }, saying, \uc1\u8216*For I have asked him of the {\scaps Lord}.\uc1\u8217*
