{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
And a bribe destroyeth the character.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 8}The end of a thing is better than the beginning,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
And the patience is better than pride.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 9}Do not be hastily vexed in thy temper;
