{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 30}Then there came to Jeremiah this message from {\super\cf2\fs24 31}Jehovah: Send to all the exiles and say, Thus saithJehovah concerning Shemaiah of Nehelam: Shemaiahhas been prophesying to you without any commission {\super\cf2\fs24 32}from Me and has made you trust in a lie. For thisreason, therefore\uc1\u8211* thus saith Jehovah \uc1\u8211* I will punishShemaiah of Nehelam and his descendants: not aman shall he have among you who will ever see the goodfortune I will bring you, saith Jehovah: for his wordsare a disloyalty to Jehovah.
