{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
And no rest she findeth.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
In the midst of her straits her pursuers
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
Have all overtaken her.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 4}The highways to Zion lie mourning,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
For pilgrims are none.
\par}

