{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
For the bread they searched in their need,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
But their search was in vain.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 20}Look, Lord, for distress is upon me,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
And ferment within me.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Within me my heart writhes with pain,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
That, for playing the rebel,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
The sword dealeth death in the streets,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
In the houses the pestilence.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 21}Listen to these my sighs;
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
There is no one to comfort me.
