{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
{\cf1 1}The word of Jehovah to Hosea the son of Beeri in the days of Uzziah, Jotham, Aiiaz, and Hezekiah, kings of Judah and in the days of Jeroboam, son of Joash, king of Israel. 
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
{\super\cf2\fs24 2}Now Jehovah said to Hosea:
\par}

