{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
That I will break the bow of Israel in the valley of Jezreel.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 6}And when she conceived again and bore a daughter, he said to him:
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Call her name <<Unpitied,>>
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
For I will no longer
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Have pity on the house of Israel.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
That I should still spare them.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 
\par}

