{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 20}On that day there will be inscribed upon the bells of the horses, \uc1\u8220*Holy to the {\scaps Lord}\uc1\u8221* and the pots in the house of the {\scaps Lord} will be as holy as the sacrificial bowls before the altars. {\super\cf2\fs24 21}Every pot in Jerusalem and in Judah will be holy to the {\scaps Lord} of hosts and all who sacrifice will come and take of them and cook the sacrifices in them. There will be no more traffickers in the house of the {\scaps Lord} of hosts in that day.
