{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 16}\uc1\u8216*And, when you fast, do not put on gloomy looks, as hypocrites do who disfigure their faces so that they may be seen by people to be fasting. That, I tell you, is their reward! {\super\cf2\fs24 17}But, when one of you fasts, they should anoint their head and wash their face, {\super\cf2\fs24 18}so that they may not be seen by people to be fasting, but by their Father who dwells in secret; and their Father, who sees what is secret, will reward them.
