{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 24}\uc1\u8216*Everyone, therefore, who listens to this teaching of mine and acts on it may be compared to a prudent person, who built their house on the rock. {\super\cf2\fs24 25}The rain poured down, the rivers rose, the winds blew and beat on that house, but it did not fall, for its foundations were on the rock. {\super\cf2\fs24 26}Everyone who listens to this teaching of mine and does not act on it may be compared to a foolish person, who built their house on the sand. {\super\cf2\fs24 27}The rain poured down, the rivers rose, the winds blew and struck against that house, and it fell with a great crash.\uc1\u8217*
