{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 46}\uc1\u8216*Somebody touched me,\uc1\u8217* said Jesus, \uc1\u8216*for I felt that power had gone out from me.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 47}Then the woman, when she saw that she was discovered, came forward trembling, and threw herself down before him; and, in the presence of all the people, she told him her reason for touching him, and that she had been cured instantly.
