{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
\uc1\u8216*Do not weep,\uc1\u8217* Jesus said, \uc1\u8216*she is not dead; she is asleep.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 53}They began to laugh at him, for they knew that she was dead. {\super\cf2\fs24 54}But, taking her by the hand, Jesus said in a loud voice, \uc1\u8216*Child, rise!\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 55}The child\uc1\u8217*s spirit returned to her, and she instantly stood up; and Jesus ordered them to give her something to eat. {\super\cf2\fs24 56}Her parents were amazed, but Jesus impressed on them that they were not to tell anyone what had happened. 
