{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 7}Prince Herod heard of all that was happening, and was perplexed, because it was said by some that John must be risen from the dead. {\super\cf2\fs24 8}Some again said that Elijah had appeared, and others that one of the old prophets had risen again. {\super\cf2\fs24 9}But Herod himself said, \uc1\u8216*John I beheaded; but who is this of whom I hear such things?\uc1\u8217* And he endeavoured to see him.
