{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 18}Afterwards, when Jesus was alone, praying, his disciples joined him, and he asked them this question \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8216*Who do the people say that I am?\uc1\u8217*
