{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 19}\uc1\u8216*John the Baptist,\uc1\u8217* was their answer. \uc1\u8216*Others, however, say that you are Elijah, while others say that one of the old prophets has risen again.\uc1\u8217*
