 {\super\cf2\fs24 58}\uc1\u8216*Foxes have holes,\uc1\u8217* he replied, \uc1\u8216*and wild birds their nests, but the Son of Man has nowhere to lay his head.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 59}To another man Jesus said, \uc1\u8216*Follow me.\uc1\u8217*
