{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 61}\uc1\u8216*Master,\uc1\u8217* said another, \uc1\u8216*I will follow you; but first let me say goodbye to my family.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 62}But Jesus answered, \uc1\u8216*No one who looks back, after putting their hand to the plough, is fitted for the kingdom of God.\uc1\u8217* 
