 {\super\cf2\fs24 23}Then, turning to his disciples, Jesus said to them alone, \uc1\u8216*Blessed are the eyes that see what you are seeing; {\super\cf2\fs24 24}for, I tell you, many prophets and kings wished for the sight of the things which you are seeing, yet never heard them.\uc1\u8217*
