 {\super\cf2\fs24 26}\uc1\u8216*What is said in the Law?\uc1\u8217* answered Jesus. \uc1\u8216*What do you read there?\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 27}His reply was \uc1\u8211*
