{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi0 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 28}\uc1\u8216*You have answered right,\uc1\u8217* said Jesus, \uc1\u8216*Do that, and you will live.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 29}But the man, wanting to justify himself, said to Jesus, \uc1\u8216*And who is my neighbour?\uc1\u8217*
