{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 37}\uc1\u8216*The one that took pity on him,\uc1\u8217* was the answer; at which Jesus said, \uc1\u8216*Go and do the same yourself.\uc1\u8217*
