{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 38}As they continued their journey, Jesus came to a village, where a woman named Martha welcomed him to her house. {\super\cf2\fs24 39}She had a sister called Mary, who seated herself at the Master\uc1\u8217*s feet, and listened to his teaching; {\super\cf2\fs24 40}but Martha was distracted by the many preparations that she was making. So she went up to Jesus and said, \uc1\u8216*Master, do you approve of my sister\uc1\u8217*s leaving me to make preparations alone? Tell her to help me.\uc1\u8217*
