{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 41}\uc1\u8216*Martha, Martha,\uc1\u8217* replied the Master, \uc1\u8216*you are anxious and trouble yourself about many things; {\super\cf2\fs24 42}but only a few are necessary, or rather one. Mary has chosen the good part, and it will not be taken away from her.\uc1\u8217* 
