{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\cf1 11}One day Jesus was at a certain place praying, and, when he had finished, one of his disciples said to him, \uc1\u8216*Master, teach us to pray, as John taught his disciples.\uc1\u8217*
