{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 34}\uc1\u8216*Do you ask me that yourself?\uc1\u8217* replied Jesus, \uc1\u8216*or did others say it to you about me?\uc1\u8217*
