 {\super\cf2\fs24 35}\uc1\u8216*Do you take me for a Jew?\uc1\u8217* was Pilate\uc1\u8217*s answer. \uc1\u8216*It is your own nation and the chief priests who have given you up to me. What have you done?\uc1\u8217*
