{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 36}\uc1\u8216*My kingly power,\uc1\u8217* replied Jesus, \uc1\u8216*is not due to this world. If it had been so, my servants would be doing their utmost to prevent my being given up to the authorities; but my kingly power is not from the world.\uc1\u8217*
