{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 37}\uc1\u8216*So you are a king after all!\uc1\u8217* exclaimed Pilate. \uc1\u8216*Yes, it is true I am a king,\uc1\u8217* answered Jesus. \uc1\u8216*I was born for this, I have come into the world for this \uc1\u8211* to bear testimony to the truth. Everyone who is on the side of truth listens to my voice.\uc1\u8217*
