 {\super\cf2\fs24 7}\uc1\u8216*But we,\uc1\u8217* replied the crowd, \uc1\u8216*have a Law, under which he deserves death for making himself out to be the Son of God.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 8}When Pilate heard what they said, he became still more alarmed; {\super\cf2\fs24 9}and, going into the Government house again, he said to Jesus, \uc1\u8216*Where do you come from?\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 10}But Jesus made no reply. So Pilate said to him, \uc1\u8216*Do you refuse to speak to me? Don\uc1\u8217*t you know that I have power to release you, and have power to crucify you?\uc1\u8217*
