\uc1\u8216*What! Should I crucify your king?\uc1\u8217* exclaimed Pilate. \uc1\u8216*We have no king but the Emperor,\uc1\u8217* replied the chief priests; {\super\cf2\fs24 16}so Pilate gave Jesus up to them to be crucified.
