{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 16}\uc1\u8216*Mary!\uc1\u8217* said Jesus. She turned round, and exclaimed in Hebrew, \uc1\u8216*Rabboni!\uc1\u8217* (or, as we should say, \uc1\u8220*teacher\uc1\u8221*). {\super\cf2\fs24 17}\uc1\u8216*Do not hold me,\uc1\u8217* Jesus said, \uc1\u8216*for I have not yet ascended to the Father. But go to my brothers, and tell them that I am ascending to him who is my Father and their Father, my God and their God.\uc1\u8217* {\super\cf2\fs24 18}Mary of Magdala went and told the disciples that she had seen the Master, and that he had said this to her.
