 {\super\cf2\fs24 24}But Thomas, one of the Twelve, called \uc1\u8220*The Twin,\uc1\u8221* was not with them when Jesus came; {\super\cf2\fs24 25}so the rest of the disciples said to him, \uc1\u8216*We have seen the Master!\uc1\u8217*
