\uc1\u8220*I will live among them, and walk among them;
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
And I will be their God, and they will be my people.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 17}Therefore \uc1\u8216*Come out from among the nations, and separate yourselves from them,\uc1\u8217* says the Lord,
