\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\cf1 15}Then I saw another portent in the heavens \uc1\u8211* a great and marvellous portent \uc1\u8211* seven angels with the seven last curses; because with them the wrath of God is ended.
