\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi720 
 {\cf1 19}After this, I heard what seemed to be a great shout from a vast throng in heaven, crying \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\cf2\fs24 1}\uc1\u8220*Hallelujah! To our God belong salvation, and glory, and Power, {\super\cf2\fs24 2}for true and righteous are his judgments. For he has passed judgment on the Great Harlot who was corrupting the earth by her licentiousness, and he has taken vengeance on her for the blood of his servants.\uc1\u8221*
