{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi0 
 {\super\cf2\fs24 3}Again they cried \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*Hallelujah!\uc1\u8221* And the smoke from her ruins rises for ever and ever. {\super\cf2\fs24 4}Then the twenty-four elders and the Four creatures prostrated themselves and worshiped God who was seated on the throne, crying \uc1\u8211* \uc1\u8220*Amen, Hallelujah!\uc1\u8221*; {\super\cf2\fs24 5}and from the throne there came a voice which said \uc1\u8211*
